{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"storage_map","type":"text","text":"## Storage Map\n\n**All State in localStorage вҖ” No Server**\n\n| Key | Contents | Owner |\n|---|---|---|\n| `vnme_mock_db_v7` | Course, units, nodes, items, translations, blueprints | db.js |\n| `vietnamy_dong` | Hearts, coins, streak, completedNodes, sessionCounts | DongContext |\n| `vnme_srs` | SRS cards (itemId вҶ’ interval, nextReview, counts) | srs.js |\n\n**Implications:**\nвҖў Works fully offline\nвҖў No cross-device sync\nвҖў No user accounts needed\nвҖў Clearing localStorage = full reset\nвҖў Admin CMS edits also go to localStorage\n\n---\n\n**Key Architectural Insight**\n\nThe study system creates TWO spaced repetition loops:\n\n**Loop 1 вҖ” Session-level (built into roadmap):**\n4 sessions per node Г— increasing difficulty\n= forced re-exposure with harder exercises\n\n**Loop 2 вҖ” Word-level (SRS engine):**\nIndividual vocab cards on 1вҶ’3вҶ’7вҶ’14вҶ’30 day schedule\n= long-term retention via flashcard review\n\nBoth loops work together:\nLoop 1 ensures initial learning depth\nLoop 2 ensures long-term recall","x":-1880,"y":1220,"width":440,"height":500,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"title","type":"text","text":"# Study Roadmap вҖ” Architecture Overview\n*How lessons, exercises, SRS, and gamification connect В· The complete study loop*","x":-1230,"y":-765,"width":940,"height":90},
		{"id":"unlock_logic","type":"text","text":"## Unlock Logic\n\n**getNodesForUnitWithProgress(unitId, completedNodes)**\n\nFor each node, evaluate status:\n\n```\nif node.id вҲҲ completedNodes вҶ’ 'completed'\nelse if no unlock_rule.requires вҶ’ 'active' (node_001 only)\nelse if ALL required nodes вҲҲ completedNodes вҶ’ 'active'\nelse вҶ’ 'locked'\n```\n\n**Unlock is purely sequential:**\nвҖў Only rule type: `node_completed`\nвҖў No XP, streak, or time gates\nвҖў Tests gate the next unit\nвҖў Module quizzes gate the next lesson\n\n---\n\n**Unit Node Pattern**\n```\nрҹ“– Lesson 1 (orange)\n  в””в”Җ рҹҸҶ Module Quiz (endcap)\nрҹ“– Lesson 2 (orange)\n  в””в”Җ рҹҸҶ Module Quiz (endcap)\nвҡЎ Skill: Practice Module (purple)\nрҹ“— Skill: Grammar Lesson (green)\nрҹ“– Lesson 3 (orange)\n  в””в”Җ рҹҸҶ Module Quiz (endcap)\nрҹҸҶ Unit Quiz (red) вҶҗ gates next unit\n```\n\nEach lesson node has an attached mini-quiz\nModule quizzes: 6 questions, immediate complete\nUnit quizzes: 12 questions, immediate complete","x":1040,"y":-100,"width":380,"height":570,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"lesson_startup","type":"text","text":"## Lesson Engine (LessonGame.jsx)\n\n**Startup Sequence**\n1. `session = getNodeSessionCount(nodeId)` вҶ’ 0вҖ“3\n2. `getExercisesGenerated(lessonId, session)`\n   вҶ’ generates exercises from items + session profile\n3. `getLessonBlueprint(lessonId)` вҶ’ word list for intro\n4. `lookupWords(viTexts)` вҶ’ dictionary enrichment\n5. `getNextNode(nodeId)` вҶ’ post-lesson CONTINUE route\n\n**Word Introduction Phase**\nBefore exercises: show each word one-by-one\nвҖў Large Vietnamese text + TTS audio\nвҖў English translation + POS tags\nвҖў Dictionary definition (if available)\nUser taps NEXT WORD вҶ’ START EXERCISES","x":840,"y":-890,"width":400,"height":340,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"exercise_loop","type":"text","text":"## Exercise Loop\n\n**Answer Checking (handleCheck)**\n\n| Type | Correct When |\n|---|---|\n| mcq_translate_to_vi/en | selected === answer |\n| listen_choose | selected === answer_vi |\n| reorder / word_bank | tokens.join(' ') === answer_tokens |\n| fill_blank | selected === answer_vi |\n| match_pairs | all pairs matched (auto) |\n| listen_type | fuzzyVietnamese(typed, answer) |\n| speak_sentence | fuzzyVietnamese(speech, answer) |\n\n**Fuzzy matching**: accepts no-diacritics input\nbut shows correct diacritics as hint","x":260,"y":20,"width":400,"height":310,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"hearts_in_lesson","type":"text","text":"## Hearts & Streaks (in-lesson)\n\n**During Exercise Loop**\n\nвң… **Correct answer:**\nвҖў `score++`\nвҖў `currentStreak++`\nвҖў Streak milestones: `streak_3`, `streak_5`\nвҖў `bestStreak >= 5` вҶ’ `achievement_tonemaster`\n\nвқҢ **Wrong answer:**\nвҖў `currentStreak = 0`\nвҖў `dongCtx.loseHeart()` вҶ’ hearts - 1\nвҖў `lost_heart` notification (300ms delay)\n\nрҹ’Җ **hearts === 0:**\nвҖў \"Out of Hearts!\" overlay\nвҖў Next tap вҶ’ navigate to `/` (roadmap)\nвҖў Must wait for heart regen or retry later\n\nвҲһ **testMode**: hearts = Infinity, skip button visible","x":260,"y":410,"width":400,"height":340,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"completion_flow","type":"text","text":"## Lesson Completion Flow\n\n**After last exercise вҶ’ 3 retention screens:**\n1. вҡЎ Energy bonus (+1, cosmetic)\n2. рҹҺҜ \"Weekend Quest\" complete (cosmetic)\n3. рҹ’Һ \"Triple XP Boost\" upsell\n\n**Then isFinished = true вҶ’**\n(guarded by `rewardGivenRef` to prevent double-fire)\n\n1. `dongCtx.completeNode(nodeId)`\n   вҶ’ `nodeSessionCounts[nodeId]++`\n   вҶ’ if count reaches 4 вҶ’ add to `completedNodes`\n   вҶ’ `coins += 10` (COINS_PER_LESSON)\n\n2. `addItemsFromLesson(lessonId)` вҶ’ SRS\n   вҶ’ creates SRS cards for introduced_items\n   вҶ’ `nextReview = today` (due immediately)\n   вҶ’ existing items NOT reset\n\n3. Notifications: `lesson_complete` (+400ms)\n   `coins_earned` (+2000ms)\n\n**Finish screen:**\nвҖў Score: X/N correct\nвҖў Words learned list\nвҖў CONTINUE вҶ’ next node route or `/`","x":260,"y":845,"width":400,"height":470,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"test_types","type":"text","text":"## Tests & Quizzes (UnitTest.jsx)\n\n**Two Quiz Modes**\n\nрҹҸҶ **Module Quiz** (`test_scope: 'module'`)\nвҖў Source: `getExercisesForNode(nodeId)`\n  вҶ’ fetches source lesson's exercises\nвҖў Size: 6 questions, shuffled\nвҖў Completion: immediate (no 4-session req)\nвҖў Reward: 25вӮ«\nвҖў Unlocks: next lesson node\n\nрҹ“Ӣ **Unit Quiz** (`test_scope: 'unit'`)\nвҖў Source: `getExercisesForUnit(unitId)`\n  вҶ’ ALL lessons in the entire unit\nвҖў Size: 12 questions, shuffled\nвҖў Completion: immediate\nвҖў Reward: 25вӮ«\nвҖў Unlocks: next unit's first node\n\nSame exercise types as LessonGame\nNo retention screens вҖ” direct to finish","x":260,"y":1470,"width":400,"height":370,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"srs_system","type":"text","text":"## Spaced Repetition System (srs.js)\n\n**SRS Storage** вҶ’ localStorage `vnme_srs`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"it_w_0001\": {\n    itemId: \"it_w_0001\",\n    vietnamese: \"xin chГ o\",\n    english: \"hello (polite)\",\n    intervalIndex: 2,\n    nextReview: \"2026-03-09\",\n    lastReview: \"2026-03-02\",\n    correctCount: 4,\n    wrongCount: 1\n  }\n}\n```\nFlat object keyed by itemId\nNew items: `intervalIndex: 0, nextReview: today`\n\n---\n\n**SM-2 Simplified Algorithm**\n\nIntervals: `[1, 3, 7, 14, 30]` days\n\n```\nвң… Correct:\n  intervalIndex = min(intervalIndex + 1, 4)\n  nextReview = today + INTERVALS[newIndex]\n\nвқҢ Wrong:\n  intervalIndex = 0  вҶҗ reset!\n  nextReview = today + 1 day\n```\n\nNo ease factor (unlike full SM-2)\nEvery correct answer advances by exactly 1 level\n\n**Progression timeline example:**\nDay 1 вҶ’ Day 2 вҶ’ Day 5 вҶ’ Day 12 вҶ’ Day 26 вҶ’ Day 56\n\n---\n\n**Integration Points**\n\nрҹ“Ҙ **Items enter SRS from:**\nвҖў `addItemsFromLesson(lessonId)` on lesson complete\nвҖў Items already tracked are NOT reset\n\nрҹ“Ҡ **Due items surface in:**\nвҖў `getDueItems()` вҶ’ RoadmapTab banner\n  \"N words to review вҶ’ Tap to review\"\n\nрҹ“қ **Review happens at:**\nвҖў `/practice/vocab` вҶ’ VocabPractice.jsx\nвҖў Calls `recordReview(itemId, correct)` per card\n\nвҡ пёҸ **SRS is additive only:**\nItems never removed from the queue\nWrong reviews reset to 1-day interval\nCorrect reviews advance toward 30-day max","x":-480,"y":185,"width":380,"height":900,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"dong_system","type":"text","text":"## Gamification вҖ” DongContext.jsx\n\n**Persisted State** вҶ’ localStorage `vietnamy_dong`\n\n| Field | Type | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| `dailyStreak` | number | Consecutive active days |\n| `lastVisitDate` | ISO string | Streak calculation |\n| `completedNodes` | Set | Fully completed node IDs |\n| `nodeSessionCounts` | {id: N} | Sessions per node |\n| `unlockedStages` | Set | Stage IDs (starts w/ 'arrival') |\n| `hearts` | 0вҖ“5 | Current heart count |\n| `lastHeartLoss` | timestamp | For regen calculation |\n| `coins` | number | Дҗб»“ng balance |\n\n---\n\n**Heart Regeneration вҖ” Two Layers**\n\n**On app load (cold start):**\n`elapsed = Date.now() - lastHeartLoss`\n`regen = floor(elapsed / 30min)`\nHearts restored immediately\nвҶ’ 2 hours away with 3 hearts вҶ’ boots with 5\n\n**While running:**\n`setInterval` every 30 min вҶ’ +1 heart if < 5\nInterval cleared when hearts reach MAX_HEARTS\n`lastHeartLoss` nulled when full\n\nConstants:\n`MAX_HEARTS = 5`\n`HEART_REGEN_MS = 30 * 60 * 1000`\n\n---\n\n**Daily Streak Logic** (on mount only)\n\n```\ndaysBetween(lastVisitDate, today) === 1\n  вҶ’ streak + 1 (consecutive day!)\ndaysBetween === 0\n  вҶ’ unchanged (same-day revisit)\nall other cases (first visit, gap > 1)\n  вҶ’ streak = 1 (reset)\n```\n\nDisplayed in TopBar\nNo streak freeze yet (Phase 2)\n\n---\n\n**completeNode(nodeId, { immediate, isTest })**\n\n**Lessons (normal):**\n`nodeSessionCounts[nodeId]++`\nWhen count reaches `SESSIONS_TO_COMPLETE (4)`:\nвҶ’ add nodeId to `completedNodes`\nCoins awarded every session: `+10вӮ«`\n\n**Tests (immediate: true):**\nDirectly add to `completedNodes`\nCoins: `+25вӮ«` (COINS_PER_TEST)\nNo session counting needed","x":1080,"y":540,"width":400,"height":960,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"four_sessions","type":"text","text":"## The 4-Session Mastery Loop\n\n**Why 4 sessions to complete a node?**\n\nEach session generates a DIFFERENT exercise mix:\n\n```\nSession 0 (Intro):     Recognition-heavy\n  match_pairs вң“  |  pictures: 3  |  MCQвҶ’EN: 4\n  speak: 0       |  reorder: 1   |  word_bank: 1\n\nSession 1 (Reinforce): Balanced\n  match_pairs вң“  |  pictures: 2  |  MCQвҶ’EN: 2\n  speak: 1       |  reorder: 1   |  word_bank: 1\n\nSession 2 (Production): More output\n  match_pairs вң—  |  pictures: 1  |  MCQвҶ’EN: 2\n  speak: 1       |  reorder: 2   |  word_bank: 2\n\nSession 3 (Mastery):   Hardest types\n  match_pairs вң—  |  pictures: 0  |  MCQвҶ’EN: 1\n  speak: 2       |  reorder: 2   |  word_bank: 2\n```\n\n**Creates a built-in spaced practice loop:**\nUser must revisit the same vocabulary 4 times\nwith increasing difficulty each time\nвҶ’ reinforces retention before moving forward","x":1880,"y":1150,"width":400,"height":440,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"exercise_gen","type":"text","text":"## Exercise Generator\n\n**Session Profiles вҖ” Progressive Difficulty**\n\n| Session | Focus | Key Changes |\n|---|---|---|\n| 0 вҖ” Intro | Recognition | match_pairs, 3 pictures, 4 MCQвҶ’EN |\n| 1 вҖ” Reinforce | Balanced | match_pairs, less pictures, +speak |\n| 2 вҖ” Production | Output | no match, +word bank, +reorder |\n| 3 вҖ” Mastery | Hardest | no match/pictures, max production |\n\n**~16 exercises per session**\nDifferent mix each time вҶ’ 4 sessions feel fresh\n\n---\n\n**10-Phase Generation Pipeline**\n(in order, each phase generates N exercises)\n\n1. `match_pairs` вҖ” batch ViвҶ”En columns (sessions 0вҖ“1 only)\n2. `picture_choice` вҖ” image + 4 Vi choices\n3. `mcq_translate_to_en` вҖ” Vi вҶ’ pick EN (3 choices)\n4. `listen_choose` вҖ” audio вҶ’ pick Vi (3 choices)\n5. `mcq_translate_to_vi` вҖ” EN вҶ’ pick Vi (3 choices)\n6. `listen_type` вҖ” audio вҶ’ type Vi (fuzzy diacritics OK)\n7. `translation_word_bank` вҖ” EN вҶ’ tap Vi tokens in order\n8. `reorder_words` вҖ” scrambled Vi tokens вҶ’ restore order\n9. `fill_blank` вҖ” Vi sentence with ____ вҶ’ MCQ\n10. `speak_sentence` вҖ” Vi displayed вҶ’ record speech\n\n**Distractor pool**: sibling lessons in same unit\n\n---\n\n**Item Classification**\nвҖў \"word\" items вҶ’ MCQ, match, picture, listen exercises\nвҖў \"sentence\" items вҶ’ reorder, word bank, speak, fill blank\nвҖў \"templated\" items (contains `{PLACEHOLDER}`) вҶ’ excluded\n\n`isSentence()`: `it_s_*` or `it_p_*` prefix, or 3+ words\n\nExercise cache: `Map` keyed by `lessonId_session`\nGenerated once, reused within session","x":1640,"y":-510,"width":400,"height":860,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"data_hierarchy","type":"text","text":"## Data Model (db.js вҶ’ localStorage)\n\n**Entity Hierarchy**\n```\ncourse (1)\n в””в”Җ units (6)\n     в””в”Җ path_nodes (N per unit)\n         вҶ’ lesson_id | skill_content | test_scope\n lessons (24)\n в””в”Җ lesson_blueprints (24)\n     в””в”Җ introduced_items[]\n items (~200 words/phrases/sentences)\n в””в”Җ translations (item_id вҶ’ lang вҶ’ text)\n exercises: [] вҶҗ empty! generated at runtime\n```\n\nStored as JSON blob in localStorage\nKey: `vnme_mock_db_v7`\nFull deserialize on every read\n\n**path_node Schema**\n```json\n{\n  id: \"node_001\",\n  unit_id: \"unit_1_basics\",\n  node_index: 1,\n  node_type: \"lesson\" | \"skill\" | \"test\",\n  module_type: \"orange\" | \"purple\" | \"green\" | \"test\",\n  lesson_id: \"lesson_001\",\n  test_scope: \"module\" | \"unit\",\n  source_node_id: \"node_001\",\n  skill_content: { type, route, grammar_level },\n  unlock_rule: {\n    requires: [\n      { type: \"node_completed\", node_id: \"...\" }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Item Schema**\n```json\n{\n  id: \"it_w_0001\",\n  item_type: \"word\" | \"sentence\" | \"phrase\",\n  vi_text: \"xin chГ o\",\n  vi_text_no_diacritics: \"xin chao\",\n  audio_key: \"a_xin_chao\",\n  dialect: \"both\" | \"north\" | \"south\"\n}\n```\nTranslations: `{ item_id, lang: \"en\", text }`\nBlueprint: `{ lesson_id, focus[], introduced_items[] }`","x":-1150,"y":-500,"width":430,"height":910,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"roadmap_tab","type":"text","text":"## Entry Point\n**RoadmapTab.jsx** вҖ” The Skill Tree\n\nOn mount:\n1. `getUnits()` вҶ’ reads `vnme_mock_db_v7` from localStorage\n2. For each unit вҶ’ `getNodesForUnitWithProgress(unitId, completedNodes)`\n3. Each node gets dynamic `status`: active | locked | completed\n4. `getDueItems().length` вҶ’ shows SRS review banner if > 0\n\nRenders: vertical list of units вҶ’ nodes as cards\nProgress bar: segmented (filled segments = sessions done / 4)\nMini-quiz endcap: Trophy strip on lesson cards","x":-140,"y":-440,"width":400,"height":260,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"nav_routes","type":"text","text":"## Navigation from Node Tap\n\n**Node Click вҶ’ Route**\n\n| node_type | Route |\n|---|---|\n| lesson | `/lesson/{lesson_id}` |\n| skill (grammar) | `/grammar-lesson/{node_id}` |\n| skill (practice) | `{skill_content.route}` |\n| test | `/test/{node_id}` |\n\nCompleted nodes вҶ’ \"Redo\" confirmation modal\nLocked nodes вҶ’ no action\n`testMode` off вҶ’ all nodes show \"COMING SOON\"","x":120,"y":-1050,"width":340,"height":500,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"e2e_flow","type":"text","text":"## Complete Study Loop вҖ” End to End\n\n**The Full Cycle**\n\n```\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ  APP LOADS                                                  в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  DongContext: restore hearts (regen), update streak         в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  RoadmapTab: compute node statuses from completedNodes      в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  SRS banner: show due items count                           в”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n                       в”Ӯ\n                       в–ј\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ  USER TAPS ACTIVE NODE                                      в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  вҶ’ /lesson/{id}  or  /test/{id}  or  /grammar-lesson/{id}  в”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n                       в”Ӯ\n                       в–ј\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ  LESSON ENGINE BOOTS                                        в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  session = getNodeSessionCount(nodeId)  (0, 1, 2, or 3)    в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  exercises = generateExercises(items, SESSION_PROFILES[s])  в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  Show word intro cards вҶ’ START EXERCISES                    в”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n                       в”Ӯ\n                       в–ј\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ  EXERCISE LOOP (~16 exercises)                              в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  вң… Correct: score++, streak++, milestone notifications     в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  вқҢ Wrong: streak=0, hearts-1, game over if hearts=0       в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  Progress bar advances                                      в”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n                       в”Ӯ\n                       в–ј\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ  LESSON COMPLETE                                            в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  1. completeNode вҶ’ sessions++ вҶ’ if 4th: add to completed   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  2. addItemsFromLesson вҶ’ words enter SRS queue              в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  3. coins += 10вӮ«                                            в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  4. Show finish screen вҶ’ CONTINUE to next node              в”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n           в”Ӯ                              в”Ӯ\n           в–ј                              в–ј\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ  BACK TO ROADMAP       в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  SRS QUEUE GROWS             в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  Node progress: N/4    в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  New words: nextReview=today  в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  If 4/4: node complete в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  Review banner appears       в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  Next node unlocks     в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  User taps вҶ’ /practice/vocab в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  Repeat with session+1 в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  Correct: 1вҶ’3вҶ’7вҶ’14вҶ’30 days  в”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ  в”Ӯ  Wrong: reset to 1 day       в”Ӯ\n                            в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n```","x":-1285,"y":1220,"width":700,"height":740,"color":"6"}
	],
